00:06:24.620 --> 00:06:28.530
We're trying to set the tone at book
launch that this is about rich media.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:30.600
It's a multimedia experience.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:38.150
And if you want to take the
time to create high production

00:06:38.150 --> 00:06:38.150
video intro to your book,
you can do that,

00:06:38.150 --> 00:06:38.150
and this is what you'll see.

