was a widget.

00:08:03.250 --> 00:08:06.600
Even a simple diagram is --
we refer to it as a widget.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:10.180
A widget is any interactive
component that you have within

00:08:10.180 --> 00:08:12.440
an iBooks multi-touch experience.

00:08:12.630 --> 00:08:15.840
The next widget,
up a level in terms of sophistication,

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:16.840
is the media widget.

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:21.700
So here I have a movie,
which I can play in place, or again,

00:08:21.700 --> 00:08:23.590
bring it to full screen.

