I can tap to reveal
the transport controls.

00:08:27.030 --> 00:08:29.490
I can move around within the movie.

00:08:30.550 --> 00:08:32.360
and then pinch it back when I'm done.

00:08:32.360 --> 00:08:36.460
Next on this page I have another movie,
but it's kind of wrapped

00:08:36.550 --> 00:08:37.460
