Next in the roster is the HTML widget,
and this is your go-to widget

00:11:10.750 --> 00:11:14.410
when you want to create truly
custom interactive experiences.

00:11:14.550 --> 00:11:17.230
One thing to note with the
HTML widget is that it only exists

00:11:17.230 --> 00:11:18.700
in kind of a full-screen only guise.

00:11:18.700 --> 00:11:20.400
It can't be interactive on the page.

00:11:20.530 --> 00:11:22.790
So here we have a thumbnail
representing the full-screen experience.

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:23.940
We tap on it.

00:11:24.050 --> 00:11:27.200
After a short loading cycle,
you'll see the thing

