is fully interactive.

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:33.150
So I can strum over the different
organ systems of the human body,

00:11:33.160 --> 00:11:35.410
or tap through them, of course.

00:11:40.010 --> 00:11:41.600
And then finally we
have the review widget.

00:11:41.710 --> 00:11:44.010
As we were designing textbooks,
we thought-- or designing a tool

00:11:44.060 --> 00:11:46.570
for the creation of textbooks--
we thought it would make sense to

