Finally, at the end of the review,
I have a little summary slate

00:12:33.590 --> 00:12:37.090
that lets me know how I did
on this particular test.

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:44.400
The results of that session are
persisted until you reset the quiz,

00:12:44.400 --> 00:12:44.400
which I can do by hitting
the start over button.

00:12:44.970 --> 00:12:47.510
So that's the widget tour,
the tour of all the interactive

00:12:47.620 --> 00:12:50.890
elements that you have within the
iBooks multi-touch experience.

